  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="DA">Mercury-free gold mining - new horizons</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="DA">The project seeks to increase awareness and implement the Minamata Convention by internationally advocating for mercury-free ASGM and transferring these techniques to new countries. Ultimately, the aim is to generate funds and goodwill for projects implementing mercury-free techniques in mining communities in Africa. The project will also look at ways to create a consumer demand for &#x201C;responsibly produced gold&#x201D;.</narrative>
  </description>
